chunks.html_content:
Use this service if you’re an MOT tester and you need to:

  • record results of MOTs you carry out
  • print MOT certificates
  • buy test slots and check your test station’s balance

You need to set up an account before you can use this service.

If you have an account, you need your:

  • user ID
  • password

Call the MOT testing service desk to get help with the service.
